title: Fix Syncthing "Folder Marker Missing" Error
tags: syncthing @zettel _fix
roam-id: b72bbdb3-c6d5-4f19-ba0d-72d7dc8c9f7f
type: text/markdown

- go to the folder you want to sync
- create a new file `.stfolder`
- restart the sync process
- so syncthing will see that this is a \"syncthing folder\" and will start syncing
